<div>
  <div class="talk-to-us">
    <section class="container">
      <div>
        <h2 class="purple" id="talk-to-us">Talk to us</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="contact">
            <div class="options">
              <% unless helpers.privacy_page?(request.path) %>
              <div class="live-chat">
                <p>Live chat</p>
                <%= render ChatComponent.new %>
              </div>
              <% end %>
              <div>
                <p>Call us</p>
                <p class="telephone">0800 389 2500</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Monday to Friday between <strong>8:30am and 5:30pm</strong></p>
            <p>Chat will be unavailable from 1pm on 24 December until 29 December. It will also be unavailable from 1pm on 31 December until 4 January. Responses may be slower over the Christmas period.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Get a teacher training adviser</h3>
            <p>
              An experienced teaching professional can help if you're ready to get into
              teaching or if you're returning to teaching and qualified to teach maths,
              physics or languages.
            </p>

            <p>It may take slightly longer to be assigned an adviser between 24 December and 2 January.</p>

            <a href="/tta-service" class="button">
              Get an adviser
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
